OL,3,CSchoolboy, 11, produces special
OL,4,CRemembrance Day film using his passion
OL,5,Cfor Lego
OL,7,FAn 11-year old boy who lives near
OL,8,FGatwick has combined his passion for
OL,9,Fhistory with his creativity of using
OL,10,FLego to produce a special film to mark
OL,11,FArmistice Day.
OL,13,FJack Smith was inspired by his late
OL,14,Fgreat great grandfathers who died
OL,15,Fserving their country in' World War
OL,16,FOne.
OL,18,FHe says it's important that younger
OL,19,Fgenerations remember the contribution
OL,20,Fmade by the armed forces.
