OL,4,CRemembrance Day film using his passion
OL,5,Cfor Lego
OL,7,F"When I got these Remembrance Day
OL,8,Fcrosses in the post, then my grandma
OL,9,Ftold me to write these names on them,
OL,10,Fand that was when I first heard about
OL,11,Fthem."?
OL,13,FSpeaking about learning of his great
OL,14,Fgreat grandfathers' roles in the war,
OL,15,FJack added: "I am proud of them,
OL,16,Fbecause it must have been scary."
OL,18,FJack often watches documentaries and
OL,19,Freads books on the two world wars.
