OL,3,CSchoolboy, 11, produces special
OL,4,CRemembrance Day film using his passion
OL,5,Cfor Lego
OL,7,F"I like reading loads of books and I
OL,8,Fsometimes watch some films,"
OL,10,F"It's important for people my age to
OL,11,Freflect because if no one does, people
OL,12,Fmight forget about all this, and they
OL,13,Ffought for their lives and their
OL,14,Ffreedom."
OL,16,FJack was also interested when his
OL,17,Fgrandma told him about his great great
OL,18,Fgrandfather and how he died in the war
OL,19,Fin the trenches.
