OL,3,CSchoolboy, 11, produces special
OL,4,CRemembrance Day film using his passion
OL,5,Cfor Lego
OL,7,FIt took him 650 photos to make the
OL,8,Fvideo which he learnt to do himself -
OL,9,Fhe even did the sound effects.
OL,11,FThe project took around a week and
OL,12,FJack was keen to reflect the soldiers
OL,13,Fin the trenches.
OL,15,FAsked how he felt once he had
OL,16,Fcompleted it, Jack added: "I was
OL,17,Frelieved it was done!"
OL,19,FBut it wasn't too much of a struggle:
OL,20,F"Well I've done lots of builds before,
OL,21,Fbut that was quite big to do."
