OL,7,FSpeaking about his achievement Jack's
OL,8,Fmum Bekka Smith said she didn't even
OL,9,Fknow he was doing it: "He was hidden
OL,10,Faway in his bedroom.
OL,12,F"I started watching it and I was
OL,13,Fintrigued in all the detail.
OL,15,F"I was really impressed. I didn't know
OL,16,Fit was going to be so long and all the
OL,17,Fdetail and there was even a little rat
OL,18,Frunning around.
OL,20,F"He enjoys his own imagination and
OL,21,Fbringing true life events to life.
